query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_orgs,
  SUM(CASE WHEN orgName LIKE '%test%' OR orgName LIKE '%Test%' OR orgSlug LIKE '%test%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as test_orgs,
  SUM(CASE WHEN orgName NOT LIKE '%test%' AND orgName NOT LIKE '%Test%' AND orgSlug NOT LIKE '%test%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as real_orgs
FROM organizations;
